  "steps": [
    "Make incisions on pomfrets and transfer into a bowl. Add salt, lemon juice and ½ teaspoon Kashmiri red chilli powder and mix well. Set aside for 20 minutes.",
    "Take ginger-garlic paste in a bowl, add yogurt, carom seeds, roasted gram flour, dried fenugreek leaves powder, garam masala powder, ½ teaspoon Kashmiri red chilli powder and mustard oil and whisk well.Apply this marinade all over the fish and set aside to marinate for 1 hour.",
    "Preheat the air fryer at 180° C for 3 minutes.",
    "Cover the air fryer basket with aluminium foil and arrange the pomfrets in it. Fit the basket into the air fryer and air fry for 10 minutes. Bring the basket out, flip the pomfrets, apply some butter on them. Fit the basket into the air fryer and air fry for 3 minutes more.",
    "Bring the basket out again, transfer the pomfrets onto a serving plate and serve hot with green chutney, onion rings and mint sprigs."
